Class I2cDeviceOnI2cDeviceController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ftccommunity.i2clibrary.I2cDeviceOnI2cDeviceController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware.HardwareDevice, II2cDevice 

    public final class I2cDeviceOnI2cDeviceController
extends java.lang.Object
implements II2cDevice
    This is almost identical to I2cDevice, but it implements an the II2cDevice interface, thus supporting polymorphism with NXT I2C devices
